		{
			"id":"bdeba9a038bb0c92",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"## [[CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Sharing)]]\n\n- customize the SOP cross-origin behavior, relaxing or hardening SOP for specific scenarios\n\nAllows to specify:\n- a whitelist of trusted domains\n- a what HTTP methods are allowed\n- a what headers to send\n- a whether to attach cookies or not",
