			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"## [[COEP (Cross-Origin Embedder Policy)]]\n\nCOEP ensures that resources loaded from other sources have explicitly given permission to be embedded\n- Only resources that come from an HTTP response presenting the required headers are allowed to be embedded",
